gin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;微信的产品经理&amp;nbsp;Genie&amp;nbsp;Lin&amp;nbsp;补充道，她曾经参与过&amp;nbsp;QQ&amp;nbsp;邮箱的开发工作。QQ&amp;nbsp;邮箱是一个中国的电子邮件服务网站，其创始人&amp;nbsp;Allen&amp;nbsp;Zhang&amp;nbsp;同时也是微信的开发者。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;Genie&amp;nbsp;Lin&amp;nbsp;表示你首先需要知道你想要达到的目标原则，进而才能做出决定。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;聊天应用的核心价值&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-a