t;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;米袋子，菜篮子，果盘子，消费升级必然使得某种业态备受关注。主打生鲜的永辉刚一出来的时候也是火得一塌糊涂，现在依旧受到资本青睐。关键在于你做得是否专业，成长性怎么样。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;9、红旗连锁连下两城&amp;nbsp;收购红艳和互惠&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;作为便利店第一股，红旗连锁今年开启扩张模式，先后用2.38亿元、3.49亿元分别收购了成都红艳超市和四川互惠商业。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;3月18日，红旗连锁发布公告称，公司使用自有资金2.38亿元收购成都红艳超市有限公司的超市业务相关资产，包括红艳超市位于成都市温江区成都海峡两岸科技产业开发园新华大道一段45号的房产及所有地面附着物及设施设备、运输车辆等，以及红艳超市125家直营门店使用权及其门店内的设施、设备的所有权。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;彼时，红旗连锁董事长曹世如表示，一旦红旗连锁成功整合红艳超市，将在并购道路上继续尝试，“走出第一步，肯定会有第二步。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;随后，7月6日，红旗连锁发布公告称，3.49亿元收购四川省互惠商业有限责任公司、成都市互惠实业有限责任公司及崇州市互惠生态农业有限责任公司共同持有的成都市互惠超市有限责任公司100%股权。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;通过两次收购，红旗连锁门店总数将增至2100家，同时填补了市场空白，使得红旗连锁进一步向郫县、都江堰、邛崃、雅安、马尔康等成都周边区县，以及绵阳市、雅安市和南充市等省内二三线城市拓展。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;在经济下行的当下，有钱的跟没钱的就是不一样。收购容易，融入难。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;10、红星美凯龙&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;香港上市&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;6月26日，红星美凯龙于香港联合交易所有限公司主板正式上市，其每股以13.28港元定价，本次全球发售共计约5.44亿股股份，预计上市所得款项净额约69.06亿港元。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;红星美凯龙董事长车建新表示：“红星美凯龙在香港上市，为公司未来的发展注入雄厚的资本实力，开辟更加广阔的发展空间。公司将以此为契机，在大城市开发第二品牌，开发家装界的互联网金融，全力推进O2O平台，继续引领行业发展。”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;事实上，红星美凯龙的上市路并不顺利。早在，2012年12月它就向证监会申请在上海证券交易所上市，但在2014年被证监会贴上了“中止审查”标签。随后，红星美凯龙决定寻求在香港联交所上市，并在6月26日成功上市。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;资料显示，截至2014年12月31日，红星美凯龙目前持有158家商场，其中包括52个自营商场和106个委托管理商场,&amp;nbsp;覆盖北京、上海等一线城市和大多数二线城市。而据红星美凯龙8月26日发布的2015年中报显示，公司营业收入42.81亿元，同比增长17.4%；核心纯利11.94亿元，同比增长31.1%，毛利率更是高达74.2%。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;值得注意的是，家居市场竞争非常激烈。中投顾问数据显示，红星美凯龙市占率为7%左右。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;点评：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-para-margin-right:0.0000gd;mso-para-margin-left:0.0000gd;text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;mso-pagination:none;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;折腾了这么久重走上市路，关键是还有多少消费者去逛红星美凯龙买东西？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '');
